devdoc.author: DeTask team

getReceiversBySender().details: Get the total list of receiver’s address from the mapping `senders`. Create a new array with the total counted. Add the receiver's info to the array and return it

receiverExists(address).details: Get the receivers list from the mapping `senders`. Loop the list to check if the receive belongs to the list

params._address: receiver's address that will be verified

receiversCountBySender().details: Get the array’s length form the mapping `senders` by sender

sendersCount().details: Get the numeric number from the field `totalSenders`

sendersWaitingByReceiver().details: Get the list of sender’s address from the mapping `waitReceive`

returns._0: The list of sender’s the receive need to validate

step1(address).details: Check if the receiver’s address was already on the list with the function `receiverExists`. Add the receiver’s address to the sender’s list `senders` with the unconfirmed fields `validated` and increment the number `totalSenders` in the contract. Add the receiver’s address to the waiting receiver list`waitReceive`. Transfer the money received in the function to the receiver’s address

params._address: is the receiver’s wallet address that will get the money

step2(address).details: Check if the sender’s address sent money to the receiver calling the function `senderExists`. Get the receiver’s record from the list `senders`. Update the `validated` field to true to confirm that the receiver sent the money back. Remove and reorganize the receiver address from the array `waitReceive`. Transfer the money to the sender

params._address: sender's address that will receive the money back

walletAlreadyValidated(address).details: Get the boolean field from the mapping `addressValidated` param _address is a receiver’s wallet address

returns._0: True if the receiver’s wallet address was already validated

walletValidatedBySender(address).details: Get the boolean field from the mapping `senders` receiver's array

returns._0: True if the receiver’s wallet address was already validated

devdoc.title: Used to check and validate wallet addresses before transfer task’s money
